parameters: \C[24][Becky]\C[0] The monster that attacked those warriors should be around here.
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] It seems like an evil monster, but Luuna, can you win?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I don't know. But right now, I need to learn as many rare
magics as possible. To stand against Lucia and the others.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] This flower... it's beautiful but has thorns. It's like the
flower is on guard.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The monster is very close to us now.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You're the one who inflicted serious injuries on those people.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] That is the chain of death. "Dead Chain."

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The more you resist, the tighter the magic of this chain will
constrict you. (This was a blue magic I used to specialize in... It
seems I can still use it when I'm in good condition.)
[Blaster] Ugh...! Gah...! The chain... it's tightening!

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] It's futile. The Dead Chain cannot be torn apart by someone of
your strength.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I can smell blood on you... You attacked those people's
companions earlier, didn't you?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] The moment you were captured by the Dead Chain, the outcome was
decided. You should give up.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] If you behave from now on, I won't take your life.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Damn it...! The chain came off... Dead Chain is useless... (It
seems my power hasn't fully returned yet. Not only was my magic
sealed, but I've also been weakened to this extent...)
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Luuna, did you learn the technique?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes. I learned it just as he was about to use his final move.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] This time I was lucky to learn it just as he was about to use
his move, but normally we have to wait until the enemy uses their
technique.
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] He was an incredibly strong guy.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Phew... He really was a strong enemy.

Jeff: Luuna, it's terrible. It seems Noah's condition has worsened.
Please come back to Sheena Village immediately.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Noah is!? Understood. I'll return at once.
